body:
The Official (Couple) TodoMomo Merchandise

This is the plushie from Jump Fes 2019, they’re being sold TOGETHER. AS A SET.

This one is from Kyoto Tower collaboration. It’s a keychain, made just like the picture, together.

This one is a big can badge. As you can see, it’s a couple thing ^q^ They have no chill

Also can badge but oval and more powerful.

This is a free paper fan for those who attend seiyuu event(?) I love how everyone just get random pairs on every merchandise, but there’s TodoMomo being valid 👌

This one is a matsuri merchandise line, they’re not really coupled together, but they have matching outfit ^q^

This is christmas card for christmas tree in Jump Fes 2019 ^^

This is a scene from movie, but being made into prints as a bundle of the dvd and it’s one of the TodoMomo hint in the movie, so 👌

This is the lineup of the beach merchandise for Tokyu Hands, they’re in the same beach house ^q^

.

.

.

Still have a lot more, this will keep getting updated.

title: Fun with Names
body:
Okay this popped into my head the other day and I can’t stop thinking about it, so I’m making a post!

The Japanese pronunciation of All Might’s name is

O-ru Maito

Switch the order of the words and change the pronunciation slightly, and you get

Maido Oru

Write this in kanji as

毎度折る

What does 毎度折る mean?

break every time

I’m so sorry Deku….
